---
import ArticleCard from './ArticleCard.astro';
---

<div class="bg-light-dark dark:bg-dark-dark py-2">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] m-auto md:flex justify-center">
    <div class="md:w-1/2">
      <h1 class="text-center pt-8 pb-2">Hi, I am Sarim Hasan</h1>
      <p class="px-2 mb-4">
        I am a front-end web developer from Pakistan. I have recently started
        freelancing, and you can check out my portfolio here.
      </p>
      <p class="px-2 mb-4">
        I have a passion for reading, personal growth, and sharing useful
        insights. This blog is my space to share my thoughts, provide insightful
        book summaries, and offer productivity tips.
      </p>
      <p class="px-2 mb-4">
        Feel free to contact me if you'd like to chat or collaborate on a
        project. Let's connect and discuss what's happening in the world of
        productivity, learning, and beyond! 😊
      </p>
      <p class="px-2">
        Happy reading! I hope you enjoy the website and find the content useful
        in any way.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hr border-l-[3px] border-black md:h-[300px] mx-16 my-8"></div>
    <div class="my-8 md:w-1/3 m-auto">
      <h2 class="text-[18px] text-center font-bold">Most Loved Articles</h2>
      <div class="bg-primary border rounded-[30px] m-3">
        <ArticleCard title="AI - The Future of Work" date=" January 1, 2023" />
        <ArticleCard
          title="macOS Is Boring — 12 Mini Apps That Make An “Unfathomable” Difference"
          date="June 1, 2022"
        />
        <ArticleCard
          title="Killer apps to organize your digital life - 2024 Update"
          date="March 09, 2024"
        />
        <ArticleCard
          title="Why follow your dreams - Summary of the Alchemist book"
          date="February 10, 2020"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
